ution is demonstrated\nby several numerical examples showing dynamic crack propagation and branching.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jun 2019 17:35:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 08:06:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-19"}
