stion from a 1976 Princeton math department\npreprint motivated by the Poincar\\'{e} Conjecture and finally documented in the\n1983 reference of Thurston and the second author.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jun 2019 02:54:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2020 21:34:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-30"}
