20th century. We do see some\nindications of equatorial sunspots in the observations we have from Cycle 1.\nHowever, in Cycle 2, which has much better coverage, we do not see such\nindications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jun 2019 07:54:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-27"}
